commbrd  - First attempt at a USB->RS485 converter
commdngl - USB-dongle that connects directly to a computer and delivers RS-485
ecomm    - Etchable USB->RS485 converter (proven)
ledctrlr - The main ACRIS LED controller board
ledmini  - Super tiny LED controller
libs     - Board libs
myropcb  - First run sent to Myro for production

plus a few scripts to nicely export things to my site
